rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I was relaxing on the roof at
night, gazing at the sky, when
someone stepped on me.

rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It felt like they were wearing iron
boots, and it was very painful.

rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I asked a soldier of the Superbian
Empire to find the culprit for me.

rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0004
rows.name:
But a person that strong... I
don't think anyone but Meleph-sama
could capture them.
